text: Central Coast Mariners FC is an Australian professional soccer club from the Central Coast of New South Wales. It competes in the A-League, under licence from Football Federation Australia (FFA). ==Honours== *A-League Premiership :Premiers (2): 2007–08, 2011–12 :Runners-Up (2): 2010–11, 2012–13 *A-League Championship :Champions (1): 2013 :Runners-Up (3): 2006, 2008, 2011 *A-League Pre-Season Challenge Cup :Winners (1): 2005 :Runners-Up (1): 2006 ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:A-League Men Category:2004 establishments in Australia
title: Central Coast Mariners FC
